Digging a little further, the Notification plugin is posting the following:

```
{
  "name": "818b5a544998ebee78592280c9f1de16",
  "url": "job/818b5a544998ebee78592280c9f1de16/",
  "build": {
    "number": 17,
    "phase": "STARTED",
    "url": "job/818b5a544998ebee78592280c9f1de16/17/",
    "parameters": {
      "JANKY_ID": "20",
      "JANKY_SHA1": "737b877e"
    }
  }
}
```

[janky/builder/payload.rb](https://github.com/github/janky/blob/master/lib/janky/builder/payload.rb#L11) expects there to be a **full_url** field under **build**, but from the JSON, there is no **full_url** just **url**.

